Title: Little Fockers Official Trailer #1 - (2010) HD
Comment: Its hard to dislike this movie, but it does fall into the all too familiar sequel pitfalls, such as introducing new characters. It had been 6 years since the previous chapter of the Fockers, and the gags are quite strained and the actors look tired of playing the same characters. Even though it was good to see all the cast members back for one last try at making us laugh,  Dustin Hoffman had refused to be a part of this movie and that's why he doesn't appear in a good portion it. It was Barbra Streisand who finally got him to come on board half way through the filming so the writers had to scramble to put Bernie Focker back into the movie.
